HMO-LOBBY ( Washington ) _ A look at the high-stakes lobbying surrounding the HMO debate as House Republicans prepare a final draft of a bill and Democrats step up the pressure , looking to score political points .
Insurance groups launch a new set of radio and print ads and mobilize business leaders .
